    <item>
      <title>Zee 与索尼印度就合并交易失败达成法律和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/zee-sony-india-settle-legal-dispute-over-collapsed-merger-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zee Entertainment Enterprises Ltd. 宣布与索尼影视网络印度公司 (Sony Pictures Networks India) 的法律纠纷达成和解后，其股价出现上涨，最终为因合并失败而引发的企业争斗拉下了帷幕，此次合并原本会催生出一家媒体巨头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-27/zee-sony-india-settle-legal-dispute-over-collapsed-merger-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 27 Aug 2024 10:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
